description:
PmEventM:  Table containing performance management event data for Ericsson radio access network cells, including timestamp, cell location, identifier, data type, and version information.
- dateTime: Timestamp of the performance management event.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographic area where the cell is located.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
- Id2:  Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  Generic identifier (appears constant in sample data).
- vsDataType: Type of performance management data.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- PmEventM.pmEventMId: Unique identifier for the specific performance management event record.
